				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="service-item">
				<h3 class="service-item-title"><b>pro bono</b><br /> technology<br /> initiatives</h3>
				<p class="service-item-text">
					Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quisquam, quos.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="service-item">
